#eNCA speaks to Hector Bartlett, the son of award-winning veteran actor Jamie Bartlett. #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Actor Jamie Bartlett has been described as a passionate man by his son, Hector Bartlett. The family has confirmed that the 55-year-old actor died from a heart attack on Monday. READ: Actor Jamie Bartlett passes away aged 55 Hector Bartlett says his father lived his life to the fullest and inspired him to do the same. The veteran actor is known for his role as David Genaro on the popular e.tv soapie Rhythm City. Watch the full interview in the video above. 